trans-unit.source: An inline-level flow content element that provides facilities for hosting hyperlinks within flow content.
trans-unit.target: Um elemento de conteúdo de nível interno que fornece recursos para hospedar hiperlinks no conteúdo de fluxo.

trans-unit.source: Hyperlink implements the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink.NavigateUri%2A> property that you set with the <xref:System.Uri> of the content that should be navigated to when the Hyperlink is clicked.
trans-unit.target: Hiperlink implementa o <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink.NavigateUri%2A>propriedade definida com o <xref:System.Uri>do conteúdo que deve ser acessado ao clicar no hiperlink.</xref:System.Uri> </xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink.NavigateUri%2A>

trans-unit.source: Hyperlink navigation can only occur, however, if either the direct or indirect parent of a Hyperlink is a navigation host, including <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, or any browser that can host [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] (which includes [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)], [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)], and Firefox 2.0+).
trans-unit.target: Navegação de hiperlink só pode ocorrer, no entanto, se o pai direto ou indireto de um hiperlink é um host de navegação, incluindo <xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>, <xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame>, ou em qualquer navegador que pode hospedar [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_xbap#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-xbapsharpplural-md.md)] (que inclui [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie7](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie7-md.md)], [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ie6](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-ie6-md.md)]e o Firefox 2.0 +).</xref:System.Windows.Controls.Frame> </xref:System.Windows.Navigation.NavigationWindow>

trans-unit.source: For more information, see the **Navigation Hosts** topic in [Navigation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
trans-unit.target: Para obter mais informações, consulte o **Hosts de navegação** tópico [visão geral de navegação](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).

trans-unit.source: Hyperlink enforces a strong content model for child content.
trans-unit.target: Hiperlink impõe um modelo de conteúdo de alta segurança para o conteúdo filho.

trans-unit.source: See [TextElement Content Model Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for more information about the Hyperlink content model.
trans-unit.target: Consulte [visão geral do modelo de conteúdo TextElement](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) para obter mais informações sobre o modelo de conteúdo do hiperlink.

trans-unit.source: If the value of the NavigateUri property changes after the user clicks the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> and before the subsequent navigation request, <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink> ignores the new value of the NavigateUri property and navigates to the [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uri](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uri-md.md)] that was the value of the NavigateUri property when the user clicked the <xref:System.Windows.Documents.Hyperlink>.

trans-unit.source: > [!IMPORTANT] > Depending on the host computer's security configuration, certain forms of navigation (for example, navigating to a [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_unc](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-unc-md.md)] path) are not allowed in the Internet zone.
trans-unit.target: > [!IMPORTANT] > Dependendo da configuração de segurança do computador host, certas formas de navegação (por exemplo, navegando até um [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_unc](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-unc-md.md)] caminho) não são permitidos na zona da Internet.

trans-unit.source: In such cases, this method will demand full trust.
trans-unit.target: Nesses casos, esse método exigem confiança total.

trans-unit.source: For more information, see [Code Access Security](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md).
